properties.Name: GeneralOverheadBudget
properties.Description:
Overhead costs are resources consumed for purposes which are incidental to, but necessary to, the production, sales and support of products and services.

Ex:
- Utilities
- Rent
- Insurance
- Indirect material

Columns.Name: BudgetedTotalOverheadCostsAmount
Columns.Description: The budgeted/planned overhead costs for the associated period.

Columns.Description: The actual overhead costs for the associated period.
